{"tid":1383117,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[醫護] 728 西環, 警方似乎使用了 DM 催淚氣體","createTime":"2019-07-29T15:33:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-30T13:38:58.000Z","uid":201889,"like":86,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":31,"replies":[{"pid":"a5c59f57650a54dd635b7988f40c10885b397d3d","tid":1383117,"uid":201889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T15:33:21.000Z","msg":"警方似乎使用了 DM 催淚氣體 <span style=\"color: gold;\">DM : diphenylaminearsine</span><br />\n<br />\n[人肉翻譯, 專業人士請協助改正]<br />\n<br />\n接觸低劑量人士, 反應會如重感冒(severe cold)<br />\n病徵一般會在 20分鐘-2小時內消失, 沒有長遠效果<br />\n<br />\n但曾接觸大劑量化學品的人士, 可能會有更大的身體反應, 如出現嚴重不適, 可能需要醫療支援 (supportive measure for symptomatic complaints)<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n病徵會有 :<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"></span><br />\n<br />\n初時有 作嘔 的感覺<br />\n<br />\n接觸後 20-30分鐘是強烈的反胃 和 嘔吐<br />\n同時可能連續數小時會有 :<br />\n- 出汗<br />\n- 發冷<br />\n- 頭痛<br />\n- 腹部绞痛<br />\n- 肚瀉<br />\n- 全身乏力<br />\n- 情緒低落<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<ins>DM 對呼吸系統的影響 :</ins><br />\n<br />\n- 大量分泌鼻水和口水<br />\n- 喉嚨熱 (burning in the throat)<br />\n- 不能自控的 打喷嚏 和 咳嗽<br />\n- 鼻塞及上呼吸道閉塞, 做成窒息的感覺<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<ins>DM 對皮膚的影響 :</ins><br />\n<br />\n此化學品主要是影響呼吸及腸胃<br />\n皮膚會有不適 (irritation) 及 變紅 (redness), 但應很快退去<br />\n<br />\n接觸到大劑量的 DM 時, 皮膚會出現持續的發紅, 痕癢, 腫脹 及 出水泡.<br />\n嚴重的皮膚感染, 需要尋求治療協助 (may require symptomatic treatment)<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n清除污染 :<br />\n<br />\n- 戴著防毒面具及眼罩, 將衣物及頭髮的化學品乾粉拍走<br />\n- 化學品會黏在有汗或濕的衣物上, 要盡快更衣及用大量清水及肥皂 (soap) 洗澡<br />\n- 注意洗頭髮時要閉上眼睛, 及面向下, 以免化學品隨水入眼<br />\n<br />\n- 如入眼睛, 以大量溫水沖洗最少 15分鐘<br />\n<br />\n- 若清洗受污染衣物時要用凍水, 以免化學品氣化<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n[編者按]<br />\n<br />\n文件沒有提如何處理身體的不適, 似乎應在一天內自動退去<br />\n<span style=\"color: violet;\">如徵狀持續, 請盡快尋求醫生協助</span><br />\n<br />\n如當時沒有全面清潔, 建議更換清洗 床單被套, 浴巾, 眼鏡, 避免殘留化學品引起二次感染<br />\n留意未清洗前, 要將曾接觸過化學品的衣物, 行李 用膠袋包好<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nSource :<br />\n&quot;How to deal with tear gas&quot;<br />\n<a href=\"https://democrati.net/2011/11/21/how-to-deal-with-tear-gas/?fbclid=IwAR1ModAWgZamanpRDHTZc3fgW_ooLl3WoXafh6agzL8I3Tw0IRF2ArPNfkc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdemocrati.net%2F2011%2F11%2F21%2Fhow-to-deal-with-tear-gas%2F%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR1ModAWgZamanpRDHTZc3fgW_ooLl3WoXafh6agzL8I3Tw0IRF2ArPNfkc&d=BhuSHdI33QWLqsaIYsxmJUtjIx4W8g%2FGk507jgkcous%3D&h=c40c922e\" target=\"_blank\">https://democrati.net/2011/11/21/how-to-deal-with-tear-gas/?fbclid=IwAR1ModAWgZamanpRDHTZc3fgW_ooLl3WoXafh6agzL8I3Tw0IRF2ArPNfkc</a><br />\n<br />\nCDC Emergency Response to DM<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.cdc.gov/niosh/ershdb/emergencyresponsecard_29750017.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cdc.gov%2Fniosh%2Fershdb%2Femergencyresponsecard_29750017.html&d=BhuSHdI33QWLqsaIYsxmJUtjIx4W8g%2FGk507jgkcous%3D&h=9b1c1b4b\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.cdc.gov/niosh/ershdb/emergencyresponsecard_29750017.html</a>"},{"pid":"14d7e78c7f98301061bc85fa47fbcff4e5f8a617","tid":1383117,"uid":30966,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T15:41:18.000Z","msg":"冇人推？"},{"pid":"6d14c9197b9bcba7651f22584bf35aa35e007e11","tid":1383117,"uid":265662,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T15:41:58.000Z","msg":"班仆街"},{"pid":"5635c3fbd6951cce08bff676c872624972c12423","tid":1383117,"uid":189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T15:43:57.000Z","msg":"記者入<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有記者會記得要問<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a491ef303630cecf8f4ede3036d6787225ec11c","tid":1383117,"uid":92606,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T15:55:28.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c6f417362d1128c178beed7336ba11e030713fe1","tid":1383117,"uid":266081,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T15:58:33.000Z","msg":"有無人有收埋d罐，拎俾