the throat)<br />\n- 不能自控的 打喷嚏 和 咳嗽<br />\n- 鼻塞及上呼吸道閉塞, 做成窒息的感覺<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<ins>DM 對皮膚的影響 :</ins><br />\n<br />\n此化學品主要是影響呼吸及腸胃<br />\n皮膚會有不適 (irritation) 及 變紅 (redness), 但應很快退去<br />\n<br />\n接觸到大劑量的 DM 時, 皮膚會出現持續的發紅, 痕癢, 腫脹 及 出水泡.<br />\n嚴重的皮膚感染, 需要尋求治療協助 (may require symptomatic treatment)<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n清除污染 :<br />\n<br />\n- 戴著防毒面具及眼罩, 將衣物及頭髮的化學品乾粉拍走<br />\n- 化學品會黏在有汗或濕的衣物上, 要盡快更衣及用大量清水及肥皂 (soap) 洗澡<br />\n- 注意洗頭髮時要閉上眼睛, 及面向下, 以免化學品隨水入眼<br />\n<br />\n- 如入眼睛, 以大量溫水沖洗最少 15分鐘<br />\n<br />\n- 若清洗受污染衣物時要用凍水, 以免化學品氣化<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n[編者按]<br />\n<br />\n文件沒有提如何處理身體的不適, 似乎應在一天內自動退去<br />\n<span style=\"color: violet;\">如徵狀持續, 請盡快尋求醫生協助</span><br />\n<br />\n如當時沒有全面清潔, 建議更換清洗 床單被套, 浴巾, 眼鏡, 避免殘留化學品引起二次感染<br />\n留意未清洗前, 要將曾接觸過化學品的衣物, 行李 用膠袋包好<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nSource :<br />\n&quot;How to deal with tear gas&quot;<br />\n<a href=\"https://democrati.net/2011/11/21/how-to-deal-with-tear-gas/?fbclid=IwAR1ModAWgZamanpRDHTZc3fgW_ooLl3WoXafh6agzL8I3Tw0IRF2ArPNfkc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdemocrati.net%2F2011%2F11%2F21%2Fhow-to-deal-with-tear-gas%2F%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR1ModAWgZamanpRDHTZc3fgW_ooLl3WoXafh6agzL8I3Tw0IRF2ArPNfkc&d=BhuSHdI33QWLqsaIYsxmJUtjIx4W8g%2FGk507jgkcous%3D&h=c40c922e\" target=\"_blank\">https://democrati.net/2011/11/21/how-to-deal-with-tear-gas/?fbclid=IwAR1ModAWgZamanpRDHTZc3fgW_ooLl3WoXafh6agzL8I3Tw0IRF2ArPNfkc</a><br />\n<br />\nCDC Emergency Response to DM<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.cdc.gov/niosh/ershdb/emergencyresponsecard_29750017.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cdc.gov%2Fniosh%2Fershdb%2Femergencyresponsecard_29750017.html&d=BhuSHdI33QWLqsaIYsxmJUtjIx4W8g%2FGk507jgkcous%3D&h=9b1c1b4b\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.cdc.gov/niosh/ershdb/emergencyresponsecard_29750017.html</a>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T16:45:51.000Z","msg":"應該唔係DM... 上nonlethal technologies嗰網站，search 40mm munitions, search 40mm muzzle blast cartridge (催淚粉